pageContext.claim: “At the same time, the world is not doing well and we're going great. You look at the numbers, we're hitting highs. I get no credit for it. It’s like, when do you ever hear them talking about — we just hit 25,000 and you won't even hear a thing about it.”
pageContext.analysis: The global economy has been slowing for some time. As for the Dow, it did cross 25,000, again. It hit that mark for the first time in January 2018.
